Summary: I was driving to work when I saw this object pulsating and flying a bit low going across the high way(edens express way)
divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving to work and got on the high way when about 2 minutes in I saw this object pulsating and flying low , lower then any other that I have seen before.The reason it caught my attention was that it was moving fast , not super fast but faster then any plane or chopper that I have seen. At first I thought it was a T.V. news station reporting on traffic but I have seen helicoters before and this was not one of them, plus it made no noise??????? It flew across the high way pulsating and then I lost sight of it. After I was trying to find an explanation for what I just saw and I could not make any sense of it. This is the first time I have seen something so awesome and I was just wondering if any one else had seen this object in the sky that morning.
